# 全專案 LF line ending（避免 Windows CRLF 自動轉換在 Docker container / shell script / php / node tooling 觸發詭異問題）
* text=auto eol=lf

# 二進位檔不轉換
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tar.gz binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary

# Shell / linux artifacts 強制 LF
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
*.dockerfile text eol=lf
.env text eol=lf
